OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784225905
OL,3,CFatboy Slim: 'We were close to
OL,4,Cdisaster' after record Brighton concert
OL,6,FFatboy Slim says he's looking forward
OL,7,Fto returning to Brighton Beach "more
OL,8,Fthan Christmas" as he prepares to
OL,9,Fheadline four nights of sold-out
OL,10,Fperformances in the city that made
OL,11,Fdance music history.
OL,13,FThe DJ, whose real name is Norman
OL,14,FCook, will perform at Brighton on the
OL,15,FBeach from Thursday to Sunday - 24
OL,16,Fyears after Big Beach Boutique II drew
OL,17,Fa record-breaking crowd of almost
OL,18,F250,000 people to the seafront.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
