FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784225905
OL,3,CFatboy Slim: 'We were close to
OL,4,Cdisaster' after record Brighton concert
OL,6,FOriginally expected to attract around
OL,7,F60,000 people, the free 2002 event
OL,8,Fbecame one of the UK's most famous
OL,9,Foutdoor concerts, overwhelming the
OL,10,Fcity and prompting a major emergency
OL,11,Fresponse. Two people died following
OL,12,Fthe event, with at least 170 people
OL,13,Fsustaining injuries.
OL,15,FReflecting on its legacy, Cook said:
OL,16,F"The big one was mixed. It was
OL,17,Fbeautiful and equally scary. We were
OL,18,Fclose to disaster.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784225905
OL,3,CFatboy Slim: 'We were close to
OL,4,Cdisaster' after record Brighton concert
OL,6,F"My memories of it and enjoyment of
OL,7,Fthe day were tainted by the inherent
OL,8,Fdanger of having that many people on
OL,9,Fthe beach, but this year it's much
OL,10,Fsafer and we have enough toilets."
OL,12,FDespite those memories, the Brighton-
OL,13,Fborn DJ said returning to perform in
OL,14,Fhis hometown remains the highlight of
OL,15,Fhis year.
OL,17,F"I am looking forward to tonight more
OL,18,Fthan Christmas, almost more than
OL,19,FEngland being in a World Cup final and
OL,20,Fall my birthdays rolled into one," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784225905
OL,3,CFatboy Slim: 'We were close to
OL,4,Cdisaster' after record Brighton concert
OL,6,F"This is my favourite night of the
OL,7,Fyear. It's a celebration of the
OL,8,Frelationship I have with the city I
OL,9,Flove."
OL,11,FJoining Cook on Sunday will be
OL,12,F'Mission: Impossible' and 'Shaun of
OL,13,Fthe Dead' actor Simon Pegg, who
OL,14,Fattended the original Big Beach
OL,15,FBoutique before later striking up a
OL,16,Ffriendship with the DJ.
OL,18,F"I was at the Big Beach Boutique in
OL,19,F2002 - the one that broke the
OL,20,Frecords," Pegg said. "It was an
OL,21,Fincredible night."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784225905
OL,3,CFatboy Slim: 'We were close to
OL,4,Cdisaster' after record Brighton concert
OL,6,FPegg said Cook later invited him to DJ
OL,7,Fat another event, unknowingly giving
OL,8,Fhim an audition for future
OL,9,Fperformances.
OL,11,F"Little did I know it was a sort of
OL,12,Faudition to play at Big Beach
OL,13,FBoutique. It's an amazing
OL,14,Fcircularity...now going to be
OL,15,Fperforming there, which is kind of
OL,16,Fcrazy."
OL,18,FAlthough best known for his acting
OL,19,Fcareer, Pegg admitted performing live
OL,20,Fbehind the decks still makes him
OL,21,Fnervous.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784225905
OL,3,CFatboy Slim: 'We were close to
OL,4,Cdisaster' after record Brighton concert
OL,6,F"I find it terrifying. It's not my
OL,7,Fcomfort zone, which is why I like it,"
OL,8,Fhe said. "If you mess up, it's on you.
OL,9,FIt reminds me of stand-up comedy
OL,10,Fbecause you're in a relationship with
OL,11,Fa live audience... when it goes well,
OL,12,Fit's amazing."
OL,14,FThe four-night festival also features
OL,15,Fartists including Seth Troxler,
OL,16,FDerrick Carter, Layo & Bushwacka and
OL,17,FGroove Armada, with both Layo &
OL,18,FBushwacka and Groove Armada returning
OL,19,Fafter performing at the original Big
OL,20,FBeach Boutique events.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
